Create YOY Pointer and Format YOY color 19

STEP 1: Create a YoY Pointer.

     1. Double click on the Card visual.

     2. Card visual will display on the report

     3. Drag and Drop the â€œ.YOY rev Arrow" to the Fields Box


     4. Select Format.

     5. Select General: X position: 0    Y position: 255    Width: 70    Height: 65

     6. Turn Category: Off.

     7. Turn Background: Off.



STEP 2: Format the Pointer color    

    1. Select the Pointer card.

    2. Go to Format.

    3. Select Data Label.

    4. Select Fx button.



5. Follow the configuration below to get the Up/Down pointer looking as shown.

#808080          #CCCCCC


Make sure every think works: Select Years 2013 and 2014.

2013

 

2014
